pageContext.claim: “Dominion took out machines. That Dominion is really moving fast to get rid of their, uh, machinery. Do you know anything about that? Because that’s illegal, right?”
pageContext.analysis: Secretary of state counsel Ryan Germany replied: "No, Dominion has not moved any machinery out of Fulton County." Trump asked again: "Have they moved the inner parts of the machines and replaced them with other parts?" Germany again said no. But then Trump insisted, "They are removing machinery, and they're moving it as fast as they can, both of which are criminal finds."
